divs: Sighting Detailsme and my girlfriend saw these lights again last night. they seem like stars, you have to actually focus on a star to be able to find them, then the objects go from being a still light to a moving light, very small like a star, these objects must be very high. they move and stop changing direction, making turns and disappearing. location is in the NJ pine barrens. they are very visible without telescope or binoculars.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Woodland

Summary: star like objects stopping and turning
